JavaHelpEntry

public JavaHelpEntry()

JavaHelpEntry

public JavaHelpEntry(String name,
                     String title,
                     String startId,
                     URL help)
Construct an instance

Parameters:
name - a unique name that won't conflict with other names visible in the system. Typically, this should resemble a java package name using a domain name to qualify the space and the follow that with a particular help set name. Another choice would be to just use the URL string that points at the helpset to make it unique.
title - a title to use in the UI to describe this entry
startId - the starting help set map id to go to when this entry is selected.
help - the URL to the helpset file.
